org.hibernate.boot.model.relational

Interface MappedColumn

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Selectable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Column, ExportableColumn, Formula

    public interface MappedColumn
    Models any mapped "selectable reference". This might be a reference to a physical column or a derived value (formula)
